{"tid":707733,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【中美貿易戰】美將對華通用鋁合金板 徵收167.16%反傾銷稅","createTime":"2018-06-18T23:48:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-19T01:00:39.000Z","uid":141151,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"acf68eb82ac52e8c0bcf457aa8b4fe3b76f8a787","tid":707733,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T23:48:05.000Z","msg":"【中美貿易戰】美將對華通用鋁合金板 徵收167.16%反傾銷稅<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180619&amp;s=10793140&amp;a=58335311\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180619%26s%3D10793140%26a%3D58335311&d=vqM4mCGDxYbl5X62wekB3gdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=ad902295\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180619%26s%3D10793140%26a%3D58335311&h=c51702f9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180619&amp;s=10793140&amp;a=58335311</a><br />\n<br />\n美國一個貿易組織周一表示，美國商務部已裁定從中國進口的通用鋁合金板，以低於公平價值在美國市場上銷售，初步決定對有關產品徵收167.16%反傾銷稅。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">美國鋁業協會主席布羅克（Heidi Brock）發表聲明，歡迎商務部的決定，認為該等貿易措施「強力而具針對性」。</span><br />\n<br />\n美國商務部於去年11月對從中國進口的通用鋁合金板展開反傾銷和反補貼「雙反」調查，是商務部25年來首次在沒有企業申訴之下主動發起調查。<br />\n<br />\n美國商務部4月已初步裁定中國通用鋁合金板享有不公平補貼，將對有關產品開徵至高113%的反補貼關稅。<br />\n<br />\n路透社<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n今次夠曬針對性"},{"pid":"3648d8193c8025b09d6c06852c00cd35688cdd41","tid":707733,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T23:56:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"150bcdc96aa3f9874a8f1fb56d413e3a702363ba","tid":707733,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T00:42:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/goal.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06be1e99c579cc000f40625a044f0c8444fcb9a1","tid":707733,"uid":57376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T00:58:58.000Z","msg":"鋼材<br />\n鋁板<br />\n<br />\n下次輪到咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74769675dc33d1e6128d4158e2d7b2db7189eb78","tid":707733,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T00:59:58.000Z","msg":"一碌柒一碌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f556f6e64c03bb4011bb43680ef61fbc82f8afb","tid":707733,"uid":181727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T01:00:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/goal.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}